                      "text": "publish them"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "have them acknowledged by staff"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "review them at regular intervals"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "The absolute best way to do this is download the prewritten ISO 27001 Policy Pack and follow the guide on How To Implement Policies."
                    }
