                {
                  "text": "Yes. Whilst the ISO 27001 Annex A clauses are for consideration to be included in your ISO 27001 Statement of Applicability there is no reason we can think of that would allow you to exclude ISO 27001 Annex A 5.1. Policies are a fundamental part of any governance, risk and compliance framework. They are a fundamental part of any information security management system. They are explicitly required for ISO 27001."
