                {
                  "text": "IntranetEmailWorkshops/Training SessionsEmployee HandbooksMeetingsPostersSecurity Awareness Campaigns"
                },
                {
                  "text": "Require employees to sign acknowledgement forms.Incorporate policy awareness into training programs.Use online training modules with quizzes to test understanding."
